					Apache License, version 2.0
				</a>
				.
			</p>
			<subsection name="Jetspeed-2.1.2 Installer Distribution">
				<table>
				<tr>
					<th>Distribution</th>
					<th>Mirrors</th>
					<th>Checksum</th>
